{"tid":117993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張X輝有預謀選長隧下手 專家稱「恐怖」","createTime":"2017-02-12T16:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T01:38:25.000Z","uid":49974,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25ea677b167c0ca037d3d470241af62612a38f7d","tid":117993,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s1.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/DbXe.Oet2XNmBtAZ_lasPg--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztjaD0yODM7Y3I9MTtjdz00NTQ7ZHg9MDtkeT0wO2ZpPXVsY3JvcDtoPTI4MztpbD1wbGFuZTtxPTc1O3c9NDU0/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/39051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDbXe.Oet2XNmBtAZ_lasPg--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztjaD0yODM7Y3I9MTtjdz00NTQ7ZHg9MDtkeT0wO2ZpPXVsY3JvcDtoPTI4MztpbD1wbGFuZTtxPTc1O3c9NDU0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F39051.jpg&h=6df9bf8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/Rv5HCq2GswoYzxLYufuk6A--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztjaD0zNDA7Y3I9MTtjdz0zMTU7ZHg9MDtkeT0wO2ZpPXVsY3JvcDtoPTIwNjtxPTc1O3c9MTkw/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/39057.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRv5HCq2GswoYzxLYufuk6A--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztjaD0zNDA7Y3I9MTtjdz0zMTU7ZHg9MDtkeT0wO2ZpPXVsY3JvcDtoPTIwNjtxPTc1O3c9MTkw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F39057.jpg&h=71031667&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星島日報 - 車廂大火，冒出大量濃煙。<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】六旬狂漢聲稱兒子被害死要報仇，選擇繁忙時間在港鐵車廂縱火，繼而引火縱火，其實育有一子一女的他，兒子根本安然無恙，不排除精神病發所致。警方於事發後擔心其家人安全，登門調查證實其妻兒安全。有精神科專家指出，狂漢攜易燃液有預謀，選擇過海長隧道下手，明顯企圖與乘客「一鑊熟」，比反社會行為更嚴重、更恐怖。<br />\n　　被捕男子張X輝，六十歲，有聚賭案底，與妻及一子一女同住柴灣興民邨。家人稱，張有精神病紀錄，在柴灣東區醫院接受治療，惟經常不依時服藥，不時病發出現幻覺，自言自語稱被逼害，又稱兒子被人害死，要為子討回公道報復，雖經家人解釋，但仍大吵大鬧一番，與家人關係不和。<br />\n　　張涉在港鐵車廂縱火造成多人受傷，警方初步調查，發現他有精神病，曾幻覺兒子被害死，恐其家人有意外，即時派警員到其興民邨住所查看，證實其妻兒無恙，才鬆一口氣。<br />\n　　香港精神健康促進會主席陳仲謀表示，涉案男子選擇在繁忙時間、人多密集的車廂及車程長的過海隧道內下手，相信有預謀和部署，不只想傷害自己，明顯想與其他人同歸於盡，屬反社會行為，甚至比此更嚴重。<br />\n　　他指出，該男子涉嫌縱火，不排除是為了自殘和傷人，故不理會自己的痛楚，只想見到他人受害和慌亂。他稱，從烈火焚身情況看，傷者身體初時會有痛楚，當傷及神經後便會麻木無感覺，而腦部吸火灼熱濃煙遭燒傷，亦會麻木不覺痛楚，故他下半身陷火海時，仍屹立不倒，陳形容事件非常可怕。"},{"pid":"bc75bd774c946655314215e98be3634692b929d3","tid":117993,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:12:59.000Z","msg":"有案底點做保安？　"},{"pid":"33480bb46981cd093f61dcef1639301b6b87d34a","tid":117993,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"入咗閘 千祈唔好怯 <br />\n<br />\n一怯 你就燒春袋"},{"pid":"20cba5c2e33e7ca1d4e30e978232b00052b8375b","tid":117993,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入咗閘 千祈唔好怯 <br />\n<br />\n一怯 你就燒春袋</blockquote><br />\n屌e家搭地鐵搭到上戰場咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c2a9a18f508a8a36ba9879b81f41f8cc043b98","tid":117993,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:18:59.000Z","msg":"傻鳩燒上水就威威啦"},{"pid":"579ee75167be0e11491ee57a310bebbd0a234a76","tid":117993,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入咗閘 千祈唔好怯 <br />\n<br />\n一怯 你就燒春袋</blockquote><br />\n屌e家搭地鐵搭到上戰場咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新移民？"},{"pid":"2c0ad93f53e4d4c0a37b499dbdab0d76d5380bb7","tid":117993,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T00:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入咗閘 千祈唔好怯 <br />\n<br />\n一怯 你就燒春袋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d367ee98eab75552d487c57030b2305e01e3ab","tid":117993,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T00:51:27.000Z","msg":"唔係話前妻生個個死左咩？"},{"pid":"ccc1d39a0ec5678c6d6eefd90456